"""
        Test that the a PermissionDenied error is raised if no possible client
        identities are discovered.
        """
mock_get.return_value = []
args = 'test',
self.assertRaisesRegex(exceptions.PermissionDenied,
    'The certificate does not define any subject common names. Client identity unavailable.'
    , utils.get_client_identity_from_certificate, *args)
mock.patch('kmip.services.server.auth.utils.get_common_names_from_certificate')
